## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the potential bias in opinion pieces. The findings are based on a selection of articles and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. Additionally, the evolving nature of social norms and psychological research means that conclusions drawn here may change over time. Further empirical studies could provide a more comprehensive understanding of when honesty is or isn't the best policy.